OL,3,CDefence chief: UK not ready for the
OL,4,C'kind of full scale conflict we could
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FThe UK is not ready to defend itself
OL,8,Fin the event of a full-scale European
OL,9,Fwar.
OL,11,FLots of people have said it. But now
OL,12,Fit has come from the professional head
OL,13,Fof the armed forces, the Chief of the
OL,14,FDefence Staff (CDS).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
