OL,3,CDefence chief: UK not ready for the
OL,4,C'kind of full scale conflict we could
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,F"Since end cold war we have taken a
OL,8,Fpeace dividend, and we are not as
OL,9,Fready as we need to be for the kind of
OL,10,Ffull scale conflict that we might
OL,11,Fface," Air Chief Marshall Sir Richard
OL,12,FKnighton told the parliamentary
OL,13,Fdefence committee on Monday.
OL,15,FThe MOD budget is always stretched,
OL,16,Fbut that problem has come into much
OL,17,Fsharper focus as US President Donald
OL,18,FTrump's commitment to Nato has looked
OL,19,Fever more shaky.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
