CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F315A1768291591
OL,3,CDefence chief: UK not ready for the
OL,4,C'kind of full scale conflict we could
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FBut how quickly can the UK change its
OL,8,Fstate of readiness?
OL,10,FKnighton told MPs: "It is a statement
OL,11,Fof the obvious that we can't do
OL,12,Feverything we would want to do, as
OL,13,Fquickly as we would want to do it,
OL,14,Fwithin the context of the budget we've
OL,15,Fset.
OL,17,F"And that requires ministers to make
OL,18,Fdifficult trade-offs."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
