OL,3,CDefence chief: UK not ready for the
OL,4,C'kind of full scale conflict we could
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FThose trade-offs should have become
OL,8,Fmore apparent in a Defence Investment
OL,9,FPlan, which was due to be published
OL,10,Fbefore Christmas but which has yet to
OL,11,Fappear.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThe Plan is intended to figure out how
OL,19,Flast year's Strategic Defence Review
OL,20,Fwill be paid for and what current
OL,21,Fcapabilities may have to be dropped.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
