OL,3,CDefence chief: UK not ready for the
OL,4,C'kind of full scale conflict we could
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FAdded to that, there have been a
OL,8,Fseries of newspaper reports suggesting
OL,9,Fthat in December, Knighton told the
OL,10,Fprime minister that there was a #28bn
OL,11,Fblack hole in the spending plans over
OL,12,Ffour years.
OL,14,FThe CDS confirmed on Monday there had
OL,15,Findeed been a meeting in December, but
OL,16,Fthe subject matter was classified as
OL,17,Fsecret and he couldn't talk about it.
OL,19,FBut no one in Government has denied
OL,20,Fthose reports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
