OL,3,CDefence chief: UK not ready for the
OL,4,C'kind of full scale conflict we could
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FThe longer term outlook is that the
OL,8,FGovernment has committed to spending
OL,9,F3.5% of GDP on core defence.
OL,11,FKnighton told MPs that all of that
OL,12,Fmoney would be needed to meet the full
OL,13,Fdemands of Nato.
OL,15,FWhat everyone in the room knew, is
OL,16,Fthat the government has only committed
OL,17,Fto spending that much by 2035, at the
OL,18,Fnext of the next Parliament. As yet
OL,19,Fthere is no plan for finding that cash.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
