OL,3,CDefence chief: UK not ready for the
OL,4,C'kind of full scale conflict we could
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FSo what happens if there's a full
OL,8,Fscale war in Europe before then?
OL,10,FWell in a way there already is, in
OL,11,FUkraine. And the CDS said that so long
OL,12,Fas Russia is 'fixed' there it couldn't
OL,13,Flaunch a full scale attack elsewhere.
OL,15,FThe question is how quickly Russia can
OL,16,Frebuild its forces if and when the
OL,17,FUkraine war finishes?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
