OL,3,CDefence chief: UK not ready for the
OL,4,C'kind of full scale conflict we could
OL,5,Cface'
OL,7,FNo one knows for sure, but Knighton
OL,8,Fbelieves the UK, and Nato, have to
OL,9,Frearm quickly enough to deter Putin
OL,10,Ffrom having another go somewhere else.
OL,12,FAnd at the moment, we are not ready.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
